				<td colspan="2"><span>No &quot;Holy Trinity&quot; yet, except that Priests are pretty much required, and some people don't comprehend that more DPS (Mages and Scouts) = shorter fights and less need for heals.  In other words, many groups will look for a second healer before they will get more dps.
<br />

<br />
The BEST groups have all four archetypes, or at least Tank, Healer and other DPS.  (At this point, only some of the Scout utitily stuff is implemented, so Scouts and Mages are somewhat interchangable.)
<br />

<br />
They are also playing with the tuning all the time, so who the heck knows, really.  They just increased Priest healing power (40% increase to heals, 20% increase to the Power (mana) consumed) but then they also made some mobs INSANELY powerful with this last patch, lol.  They are gonna have to fix it right away cause people can hardly play now, lol.
<br />

<br />
Yes, I have a house, cause you need one to go Trader mode.  You get a &quot;bulletin board&quot; and hang it in your house.  Then people can go to the &quot;Brokers&quot; and search for stuff, like Bazaar.  They can then buy from the broker with a 20% markup, or they can go to your zone, visit you in your apartment/house, and buy from you.
<br />

<br />
They are going to have home tradeskill devices, and hopefully home storage as well.  And no, you don't have to cut the grass, lol.</span></td>
